  h3 3.3 - Your first comment
  p.point1 Your first comment is an opportunity to connect with potential users. If your launch goes well it will be read by!{' '}
    span.bold several hundred
    |!{' '}so it’s worth thinking about.
  img(src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/harrydry/gdmarketing/ph2.png" alt="Marketing Examples Product Hunt Comment").img__70
  h2 Step 4 - Banner time
  p On any regular day Marketing Examples averages around 500 users. I added a banner to let any passers-by know that they could support my launch.
  img(src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/harrydry/gdmarketing/ph3.jpg" alt="Marketing Examples Product Hunt Comment").img__45
