  p On the day of my launch I posted on the Startup School forum and also added a Milestone on Indie Hackers. Both posts sat at the very top for the whole day and drove considerable traffic to my launch.
  img(src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/harrydry/gdmarketing/ph51.jpg" alt="Marketing Examples Startup School Post").img__80
