  p Why were these posts so well received? Well, the best way to!{' '}
    span.bold get help
    |!{' '}is to!{' '}
    span.bold offer up something yourself.
    |!{' '}. Given I run a Marketing site it seemed suitable to share!{' '}
    span.italic some tips on how to launch to Product Hunt
    | . And I think people appreciated that. I wasn’t!{' '}
    span.italic just
    |!{' '}screaming, “Everyone, look at my startup”, but was offering some insight in return.
  img(src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/harrydry/gdmarketing/ph6.png" alt="Marketing Examples Indie Hackers Traffic").img__70
  h2 The best marketing strategy
  p I think all this stuff is well and good, but really, the Product Hunt strategy out there is having a great product. Dozens of people shared Marketing Examples on social media throughout the day.
